result_summary: Detailed yet concise description of the specific data; for tables a step-by-step explanation of how to interpret the table

evidences.location: Specific paragraph, figure, or table number
evidences.span: Exact text span from the paper that contains the result in the text; for tables, select the caption or if possible a specific cell if it contains the result

relevance_to_conclusion: Precise explanation of how this result supports specific conclusion(s)
